fault="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 49</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>come, m. to wakes and fairs,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.6.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 6, 77</bibl></cit>.
